      <h1>Meta-Writing Ecology</h1>

      <p>
        Meta-Writing Ecology is a recursive linguistic system and structural diagnostic framework.
      </p>

      <p>
        It is not ecological science, environmental research, biodiversity analysis,
        environmental writing, or a writing-advice project.
      </p>

      <p>
        Its purpose is to make structural behavior visible: how texts shape later texts,
        how instructions constrain outputs, and how meaning reorganizes under pressure.
      </p>

